kzk-10dh-xa0r,"Comptroller Hsu, I am very concerned about climate change and the lack of effort by our financial institutions to face this threat honestly and responsibly, and I thank you for this draft guidance. It outlines a framework for robust assessment, disclosure, and risk management that will force banks to reckon with climate change risk. I urge you to resist all efforts to dilute this guidance and to follow up with scope and details as broad as OCC‚Äôs authority allows. 
